ĹTo honour
Thomas J. Johnston of San Francisco
Who visited these gardens as a Commander in the
US Navy during the Normandy Landings and
later with his family and President of his company"Ń
ĺIn Loving Memory of Sarah Jane Johnson (nee Parr)
24 October. 1978 - 27 April 2015
Adored Wife, Mother, Sister, Daughter and cherished Friend
Rest in Peace Gorgeous Girl. Big Kisses x x x"Ň
¬As a small boy not far from this very spot, he began running and did not stop
Far across the globe he ran, this beloved, crazy, brilliant man
He loved wine. music and the southern sun, he always gave his best to everyone
He is much missed and that he should, for our south London boy did good
Vincent Hancock 1944-2006"Ő
